import React from 'react';
import { Container, Row, Col, Card, Nav } from 'react-bootstrap';

const AdminDashboard = () => {
  return (
    <Container fluid className="mt-4">
      <Row>
        <Col md={2}>
          <Nav defaultActiveKey="#orders" className="flex-column">
            <Nav.Link href="#orders">Orders</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#payments">Payments</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#customers">Customers</Nav.Link>
          </Nav>
        </Col>
        <Col md={10}>
          <Row className="mb-4">
            <Col>
              <Card>
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>Order Entry</Card.Title>
                  <Card.Text>
                    Placeholder for order entry functionality.
                  </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>
            </Col>
          </Row>
          <Row className="mb-4">
            <Col>
              <Card>
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>Payment Tracking</Card.Title>
                  <Card.Text>
                    Placeholder for payment tracking functionality.
                  </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>
            </Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col>
              <Card>
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>Customer Management</Card.Title>
                  <Card.Text>
                    Placeholder for customer management functionality.
                  </Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default AdminDashboard;
